defined_text = {
	name = RMT_ACTIVITY

	text = {
		trigger = {
			has_global_flag = rmt_enabled
		}
		localization_key = rmt_on
	}
	text = {
		localization_key = rmt_off
	}
}

defined_text = {
	name = RMT_RESOURCES_AMOUNT_composites

	text = {
		trigger = {
			has_resources_amount = {
				resource = composites
				amount < 1
			}
		}
		localization_key = RMT_RESOURCES_AMOUNT_0
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			has_resources_amount = {
				resource = composites
				amount < 2
			}
			has_resources_amount = {
				resource = composites
				amount > 0
			}
		}
		localization_key = RMT_RESOURCES_AMOUNT_1
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			has_resources_amount = {
				resource = composites
				amount < 3
			}
			has_resources_amount = {
				resource = composites
				amount > 1
			}
		}
		localization_key = RMT_RESOURCES_AMOUNT_2
	}
	text = {
		trigger = {
			has_resources_amount = {
				resource = composites
				amount < 4
			}
			has_resources_amount = {
				resource = composites
				amount > 2

	name = RMT_RESOURCES_AMOUNT_circuitry

	text = {
		trigger = {
			has_resources_amount = {
				resource = circuitry
				amount < 1
			}

		localization_key = RMT_RESOURCES_AMOUNT_0
